snippet.title: PAC-MAN & Galaga DIMENSIONS - N3DS - Pac-Man Tilt and Galaga 3D Impact
snippet.description:
Enjoy 2 brand new games developed specifically for the 3DS! Pac-Man Tilt and Galaga 3D Impact are new games making the most of the 3DS gameplay possibilities.

PAC-MAN & Galaga DIMENSIONS is now available on Nintendo 3DS.

Check out your local Namco Bandai games website for more information http://www.namcobandaigames.eu
